  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 375°f (190°c).",
    "in a medium bowl, crush the saltine crackers into fine crumbs.",
    "in a large bowl, cream together the butter and sugars until light and fluffy.",
    "add the flaxseed and mix until well combined.",
    "add the dashi-extract and vanilla extract and mix until smooth.",
    "add the flour and baking soda and mix until a dough forms.",
    "press the dough into the bottom of a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "drizzle the caramel sauce over the dough.",
    "bake for 25 minutes or until the edges are lightly golden brown.",
    "remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
  ],
